ads being rejected for broken LP

If your ads are being rejected due to a broken landing page (LP), it's important to ensure that the URL is correct and the page is accessible. Check for any typos in the URL and verify that the landing page is live and functioning properly. If you need further assistance, you can review our ad policy guidelines or contact adsupport@newsbreak.com for more details. Here's a helpful article on what to do next after your ad gets rejected: [My ad got rejected. What's next?](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/18085960681101-My-ad-got-rejected-What-s-next)
